le class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jrz1665702655781.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jrz1665702655781.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jrz1665702655781\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /nodebug </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Instruct Uniface to compile the application shell, component, or global ProcScript so\n      that it cannot be debugged. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__section_w2893ab1b5b1_w2894ab1b5_w2895ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__p_d150431e1_d150432e1_d150433e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/nodebug</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__section_w2896ab1b5b3_w2897ab1b5_w2898ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1215429e60\"> Used With </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__li_d52271e1_d52272e1_d52273e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sww1665702625667.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sww1665702625667.html\" title=\"Compile all types of compilable main development objects, including components, modeled entities, and global objects.\">/all</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__li_d52274e1_d52275e1_d52276e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yqf1665702625882.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yqf1665702625882.html\" title=\"Compile application shells.\">/aps or /app</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__li_d52277e1_d52278e1_d52279e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rtz1665702626248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtz1665702626248.html\" title=\"Compile dynamic server pages.\">/dsp</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__li_d52280e1_d52281e1_d52282e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ars1665702626915.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ars1665702626915.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface entity service components.\">/esv</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__li_d52283e1_d52284e1_d52285e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fvm1665702627074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fvm1665702627074.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface form components.\">/frm</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__li_d52286e1_d52287e1_d52288e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjb1665702652886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjb1665702652886.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface report components.\">/rpt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__li_d52289e1_d52290e1_d52291e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"umc1665702653094.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/umc1665702653094.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface session service components.\">/ssv</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__li_d52292e1_d52293e1_d52294e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gku1665702653234.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gku1665702653234.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface service components.\">/svc</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__li_d52295e1_d52296e1_d52297e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"prm1665702626469.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/prm1665702626469.html\" title=\"Compile static server pages.\">/usp</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__li_d52298e1_d52299e1_d52300e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ixo1665702655853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ixo1665702655853.html\" title=\"Compile global ProcScript and variables in a library.\">/lib</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__section_w2899ab1b5b5_w2900ab1b5_w2901ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1215429e170\"> Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__p_d150440e1_d150441e1_d150442e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/nodebug</span> subswitch to\n            compile application shells, components, and global ProcScripts when they are ready for\n            production and deployment.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"jrz1665702655781__note_sbl_vcr_qwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DebugPort</span> and\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">EnableDevTools</span> properties are ignored or disabled in case a\n            component is compiled with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/nodebug</span>.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfq1665702655924.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$NO_DEBUG</a><p>Determine whether to compile components, application shells, and global ProcScripts that can be debugged,</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613995\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613995\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/nodebug Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 01, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /nodebug Instruct Uniface to compile the application shell, component, or global ProcScript so that it cannot be debugged. /nodebug Used With /all /aps or /app /dsp /esv /frm /rpt /ssv /svc /usp /lib Description Use the /nodebug subswitch to compile application shells, components, and global ProcScripts when they are ready for production and deployment. Note: The DebugPort and EnableDevTools properties are ignored or disabled in case a component is compiled with /nodebug . Related Links $NO_DEBUG Determine whether to compile components, application shells, and global ProcScripts that can be debugged, Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}